Gentlemen;

These are copies of the OPORD in support of TNMAN-26, with enclosure, and
the WARNO for IDT on April 25, for your review, comment, and edits.

Since the DIV OPORD for TNMAN-26 has not been received up to this point, I
have exercised disciplined initiative to comply with the DIV CDRs intent
regarding this matter. Once the OPORD is received, I will adjust anything
that I need to with a FRAGO to our TNMAN-26 OPORD.

I regret having to "dump" all these things on you at once, but I held them
until the last possible moment as I waited for further DIV guidance.

Should you have any questions please let me know.

-- 
V/R

JOHN T. SHEAF
LTC, TNSG
S3, 3 RGT
